alStateApply,\n        KeyUWSystem, KeyApplyIdaho, KeyGAFutures, KeyCFNC, KeyFloridaSUS,\n    }\n}\n\n// All returns all registered extractors. Initially empty;\n// populated as each extractor implementation is added.\nfunc All() []Extractor {\n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n### tools/kapow/internal/platform/platform_test.go\n\nWrite tests that:\n1. Verify AllKeys() returns 13 unique keys\n2. Verify each key constant matches expected string value\n3. Verify All() returns extractors with unique keys (currently empty, but the test structure should be ready)\n\n## Quality Gate\nRun: `cd tools/kapow && go test ./internal/platform/... && go vet ./internal/platform/...`\nAlso run: `make kapow-test-unit`\n\n## Git\n- Commit all changes with a descriptive message\n- Do NOT merge to main"},"uuid":"bfaa50eb-1f9d-427f-a5c2-38d1688249f2","timestamp":"2026-03-11T05:02:54.612Z"}
